FILE TRANSFER
--------------
Transfer files via sftp (https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-use-sftp-to-securely-transfer-files-with-a-remote-server)

sftp username@server_ip

From server to local:
get remoteFile localFile

From local to server:
put localFile


SETTING UP SSH-KEYS
--------------------

(Linux)
Generate a key pair locally:
~ssh-keygen

Add the key to the authorized keys file (locally):
~ssh-copy-id username@server_ip


SERVER IP
----------

Reverse proxy ip (Droplet-1): 46.101.146.8
App-server ip (Droplet-2): 46.101.176.147


CONNECTING TO SERVER
--------------------

~ssh username@server-ip


